{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- they start, you know, shooting, and coming down and setting out fires to destroy this village.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I was, that time, underneath, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The house was burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, and a few more of us, we sort of managed to-- to-- to-- to come out of this-- of this bunker and go through the-- the-- the house was on fire.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we choked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow we got out and and we start running, running down the fields, and going back to the-- to the forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] so of course, the Ukrainians came down from these-- what did I say, not-- from these hills.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- and they all had rifles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were just, like, you know, they were hunting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just like you hunt, you know, animals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is what they were doing, running after us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And most of them got killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, next to me, my friends and their mother, there was just a few-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] maybe 20 feet away, they were killed, a mother and two-- two-- two-- daughters.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know how I escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, you know, it was a very difficult time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were just hunting, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, then we went back to the forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what I'm saying is we-- when-- we-- we were in the forest, but every time something, you know, was supposed to, that we knew that things going to come up, so we used to either change in different places in the forest, or go down to this village, you know, whoever had where to go to hide for a few days.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was going on until-- until the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was Lola Gruder and-- and Tanya Gruder, [NON-ENGLISH] Gruder.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
